    "In 2023, Shah et al. (2023) present a survey on the security features of CCN and NDN with respect to Man-in-the-middle attacks, CPA and replay attacks.",
    "Furthermore, the authors provide potential research directions in terms of security.",
    "In 2024, Anjum et al. (2024) present an overview of emerging applications for secure data communication, followed by a presentation of the concepts underlying the architecture of the NDN.",
